      "body": "It's easy. Open Synaptic package manager, open Repository properties, select \"Source\", Apply, update repositories.\n\nOpen Terminal.\n\nmkdir bitcoind-source\ncd bitcoind-source\nsudo apt-get build-dep bitcoind\ngit clone https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin.git\ncd bit[TAB]\ncd src\nmake -f makefile.unix bitcoind\n./bitcoind\n\nOpen other terminal and change working directory:\n\ncd ~/bitcoind-source/bit[TAB]/src\n./bitcoind getinfo\n",
